ChatMod

This mod provide timestamps in ingame chat with configurable formatting.
It also provide configurable chat logging in game. All configuration is done
by adding lines into minetest.conf.

Possible setting:

chatmod.time_format = <STRING>

This option allows to change appearance of chat timestamp. <STRING> can be any strftime syntax ( http://www.cplusplus.com/reference/ctime/strftime/). Default value is %T. This timeformat don't
touch format of timestamp in logfile which is in unix timestamp, to be able to process logs by
PHP or other scripts for use in webpages.



chatmod.chatlog_enabled = <BOOL>

This option is boolean value enabling chat logging. Default value is false.


chatmod.chatlog_autorotate = <BOOL>

This option is also boolean and true will enable chatlog monthly rotation. Final chatlog filename
will be YYYY-MM-chatlog.txt.


chatmod.chatlog_path = <STRING>

This option allows to change destination path for chatlog.

